  <brief_title>Effects on Glutamine on the Outcome of Allogeneic Bone Marrow Transplant Recipients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Control Studies on the Effects of Glutamine on the Clinical Outcome of Bone Marrow Transplant Recipients With Special Reference to Veno-occlusive Disease and Mucositis.</official_title>
