  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this project is to investigate if addition of glutamine, an amino
      acid, to standard parenteral nutrition, may improve the clinical outcome of the bone marrrow
      transplantation reducing the occurrence of veno-occlusive disease and severity of mucositis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
